pr_body:
### **Feature**
The PR is for **touch compatibility to CircuitVerse**
CircuitVerese just supports the Mouse on the browser till now. In this PR the website will support both Touch and mouse on Brower simultanously. 

This is Done by adding touch listeners

- 1. touchstart
- 2. touchmove
- 3. touchend

#### Describe the changes you have made in this PR -

1. Added **touch listeners** in listeners.js
2. Function for pan on the simulator is made common for both touch and mouse in listerners.js

3.**Pinch to Zoom** is implemented to zoom in and zoom out on the simulator using pinch.

Note: Please check **Allow edits from maintainers.** if you would like us to assist in the PR.

This PR is for New UI designed For CircuitVerse website Small screen version
This PR is created on the top of my first PR which is touch compatibility in which touch functionality is ad to CV.

#### Describe the changes you have made in this PR -

### Following things are changed for smaller screen
1.Circuit Element (Redesigned)
2.Properties panel (Redesigned)
3.Time Diagram (Redesigned)

### Following new things are added in this PR for smaller screen
1.Touch button menu 
2.Live button (Fit to screen, Undo, Delete)
3.Quick menu 
4.NavMenu for the small screen 
5.Portrait mode
